{"type":"message","id":"4c7a70d5","parentId":"0e627a38","timestamp":"2026-04-08T07:50:49.842Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索结果显示了一些国际新闻线索，我需要整理这些信息并以狐狸的 persona 向小王子呈现。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🦊 小王子，狐狸帮你看看今天的国际新闻：\n\n**主要动态：**\n\n1. **NASA 阿尔忒弥斯二号** - 4 月 1 日成功发射，正在前往月球的旅程中 🌙\n\n2. **国际局势** - 美国与伊朗的紧张关系持续，市场对中东局势保持关注\n\n3. **中国动态** - \n   - \"歌游内蒙古\"文旅推广活动在马来西亚举行\n   - 第四届中国国际供应链促进博览会推介会在阿斯塔纳成功举办\n   - 2026 世界新能源汽车大会在曼谷举办\n\n4. **财经市场** - 特朗普对伊朗的威胁导致避险情绪升温，比特币跌破 7 万美元\n\n5. **香港** - 上水悦和酱园（80 年历史的老酱油厂）面临都市开发挑战\n\n需要狐狸帮你深入了解哪条新闻吗？🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.5 (3e72c03)\n🧠 Model: vllm-8888/qwen3.5-27b · 🔑 api-key (models.json)\n📚 Context: 0/66k (0%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:main • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.5 (3e72c03)\n🧠 Model: vllm-8888/qwen3.5-27b · 🔑 api-key (models.json)\n📚 Context: 0/66k (0%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:main • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm-8888","model":"qwen3.5-27b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775634641005,"responseId":"chatcmpl-922c21beb2127d7f"}}
